 550 x + 350 y = 0 \\ 50 = \sqrt{ (x - 150)^2 + (y - 50)^2 }   
 (a-b)^2 = a^2-2ab+b^2 
(550x)+ (350y) =0 \quad \iff \quad 350 y = -550 x \quad\iff \quad y = - \frac{550}{350} = \left(-\frac {11}{7}x\right)\tag{1}
\quad y = \left(-\dfrac{11}{7}x\right)\quad
50 = \sqrt { { (x - 150) }^{ 2 } + { (y- 50) }^{ 2 } }\tag{2}   
